<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  <div class="flex-1 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <%= link_to root_path, class: "inline-flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-800 transition-colors" do %>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        Back
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral">
      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The McCulloughs is a private family photo gallery, built to keep our memories safe and accessible to family members.
      </p>

      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Rather than trust our photos to social media platforms that come and go, we built our own space. A simple, focused place for family photos without the noise.
      </p>

      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        Photos can be shared publicly via unique links, making it easy to share specific moments with friends and extended family.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render "shared/footer" %>
</div>
